        <abstract>
            <p>PGK’s brother is coming to England and will call on CD.</p> 
<p>He is impressed but not absolutely convinced by the <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Raises a question about which CD wrote years ago: why do sheep degenerate in Australia, necessitating periodic importation?</p>
